orking-class background. But one evening, Ben is introduced by his unorthodox math professor to a small but secretive club of five students, Jill, Choi, Kianna, and Fisher, who are being trained by Professor Rosa to count cards at blackjack.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":5.0239,"vote_count":4948,"poster_path":"/efG8Po57alqSlhqHU1lXJ3duG6t.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-27","vote_average":6.692,"backdrop_path":"/u6OCGwhSWhfQX1LZ4NTq0bfcWxs.jpg","original_title":"21","original_language":"en"},{"id":8071,"adult":false,"title":"Tout Va Bien","video":false,"overview":"A strike at a French sausage factory contributes to the estrangement of a married filmmaker and his reporter wife.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3327,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/3KLD248mlx8Ea6f6pVm0iDxpw8s.jpg","release_date":"1972-04-28","vote_average":6.58,"backdrop_path":"/uRElXqD7Dv4KypsnS1OReQS7iFO.jpg","original_title":"Tout va bien","original_language":"fr"},{"id":8090,"adult":false,"title":"Untraceable","video":false,"overview":"Special Agent Jennifer Marsh works in an elite division of the FBI dedicated to fighting cybercrime. She thinks she has seen it all, until a particularly sadistic criminal arises on the Internet. This tech-savvy killer posts live feeds of his crimes on his website; the more hits the site gets, the faster the victim dies. Marsh and her team must find the elusive killer before time runs out.","genre_ids":[53,80,9648,18,27],"popularity":1.6294,"vote_count":969,"poster_path":"/ySUwDRDEn01lKIMPQorpFCMLWqE.jpg","release_date":"2008-01-22","vote_average":6.229,"backdrop_path":"/pPTNyx5xjYQ7WX05n3eRjmhGzdC.jpg","original_title":"Untraceable","original_language":"en"},{"id":8443,"adult":false,"title":"Lower City","video":false,"overview":"Best friends Deco and Naldinho co-own a cargo boat in Brazil's Salvador da Bahia. They give a ride to a sultry prostitute named Karinna, and soon both men fall prey to her considerable sexual charms, pushing the bounds of their friendship to the limit.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4958,"vote_count":92,"poster_path":"/qFWvDBCN2LpVczu6ZKQq8B0AIYG.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-04","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/3he9tOMisKv5tEpZMl2sIyaVtVy.jpg","original_title":"Cidade Baixa","original_language":"pt"},{"id":8272,"adult":false,"title":"The Savages","video":false,"overview":"A sister and brother face the realities of familial responsibility as they begin to care for their ailing father.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.9395,"vote_count":425,"poster_path":"/nY54gSmTOmSXlQpWDB7DWp4u8a7.jpg","release_date":"2007-11-28","vote_average":6.891,"backdrop_path":"/2KoLLmYiVTBlTv0GYIJYOjYZ9s5.jpg","original_title":"The Savages","original_language":"en"},{"id":8697,"adult":false,"title":"Who Am I?","video":false,"overview":"A group of covert CIA operatives trailing a potential new energy source are double-crossed by corrupt agent Morgan, who causes a helicopter crash in remote South Africa. The sole survivor, suffering severe amnesia, is nursed to recovery by a kindly native tribe who call him \"Whoami\" after the question he keeps asking. With the help of a mysterious reporter Christine, Whoami pieces together his past and tracks the turncoat agent and his criminal cohorts.","genre_ids":[12,28,35,53],"popularity":3.8857,"vote_count":952,"poster_path":"/9YDKLbBmWGpxG5bO3TBawtNNOAr.jpg","release_date":"1998-01-17","vote_average":7.121,"backdrop_path":"/c8jufUMUxgY5cLFgOF3oNbNiHYj.jpg","original_title":"我是誰","original_language":"cn"},{"id":8391,"adult":false,"title":"When Night Is Falling","video":false,"overview":"Camille is a professor at a Protestant college and is in a long-term relationship with Martin, a respected minister and fellow professor. When Camille meets Petra, a bold and flamboyant performer in a circus troupe, she is inexplicably drawn. Pursuing Petra, Camille throws her whole conservative life into disarray.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.5971,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/6Ac5GLwJ